{"tid":853602,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"呢張相有啲咩人?","createTime":"2018-10-08T17:02:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T17:02:29.000Z","uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8f81f7439afe55278a162eb1fe30b95de9c35da3","tid":853602,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T17:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/09/005814_52e48c6810215b18237b927d9010f25f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F09%2F005814_52e48c6810215b18237b927d9010f25f.jpg&h=3d39b848&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係點五步 cap出黎，我見到有薯片，應該曾蔭權都係到?<br />\n<br />\n坐係到，左邊第4個係+x?<br />\n<br />\n睇完幾開心，曾蔭權真係時來運到，同時又有能力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相反而家佢咁，反證中共係世界大魔王，有咩運，支持，民望，都比大陸搞到雞毛鴨血<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw 點五步 好睇，值得一戲院睇"}]}